video.title: Schitt's Creek
video.synopsis: Suddenly broke, the formerly filthy-rich Rose family is reduced to living in a ramshackle motel in a town they once bought as a joke: Schitt's Creek.

episodes.synopsis: After their business manager loots their family fortune, the Rose family relocates to the town of Schitt's Creek, which they once bought as a joke.
episodes.title: Our Cup Runneth Over

episodes.synopsis: Johnny and Moira try to get on the mayor's good side so he will give them permission to sell the town; Alexis goes to a party to make her ex jealous.
episodes.title: The Drip

episodes.synopsis: Johnny tries to get a potentially offensive town sign taken down; Moira falls into a funk when she sees the results of looking up her name on Google.
episodes.title: Don't Worry, It's His Sister

episodes.synopsis: When David has wardrobe issues and Alexis is forced into community service, Johnny and Moira try to be better parents and get to know their children.
episodes.title: Bad Parents

episodes.synopsis: Johnny and Moira take the mayor up on his offer to use his cabin for a night so that they can have a private, romantic getaway.
episodes.title: The Cabin

episodes.synopsis: Moira is hired as the spokesperson for a local winery; Alexis stretches boundaries with Mutt in yoga class; David deals with a baffling health issue.
episodes.title: Wine and Roses

episodes.synopsis: In an effort to prove his manhood to Stevie, David goes on a turkey hunt with some townies; Jocelyn invites Moira on a spa day with the girls.
episodes.title: Turkey Shoot

episodes.synopsis: Moira and David try to earn easy money by selling cosmetics to the locals, unwittingly getting involved in a supposed friend's pyramid scheme.
episodes.title: Allez-Vous

episodes.synopsis: When Johnny tries to get out of being a pallbearer at a neighbor's funeral, he gets tasked with delivering the eulogy for a man he barely remembers.
episodes.title: Carl's Funeral

episodes.synopsis: Johnny and Moira attend Roland's Hawaiian bash; Ted and Alexis host a dinner; David and Stevie are uneasy with each other after their sexual tryst.
episodes.title: Honeymoon

episodes.synopsis: Moira's estranged sister, Deedee, pays an unexpected visit; Jocelyn urges David to advise a student in her class about being gay.
episodes.title: Little Sister

episodes.synopsis: Johnny plans a surprise birthday party for Moira under the guise that he is planning a fundraiser, but she wants to take control of the event.
episodes.title: Surprise Party

episodes.synopsis: Johnny finds a potential buyer for the town, but the other family members have grown surprisingly attached to the place that has become their home.
episodes.title: Town for Sale

episodes.synopsis: Alexis frets over her continuing attraction to Mutt. Meanwhile, Moira's brown bag is missing. Oh, and her only son has disappeared, too.
episodes.title: Finding David

episodes.synopsis: Moira volunteers to cook dinner, much to her family's horror. Meanwhile, Johnny searches for an office to rent and Alexis faces a dilemma.
episodes.title: Family Dinner

episodes.synopsis: Moths are having their way with David's cashmere, Moira auditions for a local musical group, and Johnny's new office has issues.
episodes.title: Jazzagals

episodes.synopsis: Mutt surprises Alexis with a thoughtful gift she can't use, Johnny and Moira storm an estate sale, and David helps Roland with his look.
episodes.title: Estate Sale

episodes.synopsis: Alexis has a cold and Moira must rise to the occasion, Johnny shares a business plan with Bob, and David enters the exciting world of retail sales.
episodes.title: Bob's Bagels

episodes.synopsis: Moira tries to beautify the town by complaining. Mutt gets a new look, but Alexis isn't a fan. David struggles with the concept of a "write-off."
episodes.title: Moira vs. Town Council

episodes.synopsis: Moira ponders a life in politics, a newly single Alexis hunts for a buddy to hang out with, and David and Stevie go drinking.
episodes.title: The Candidate

episodes.synopsis: Johnny tries the raw milk business, and Alexis reconnects with an old flame. Meanwhile, election season heats up and David is caught in the middle.
episodes.title: Milk Money

episodes.synopsis: A potential scandal puts Moira's campaign on edge, Johnny swallows a piece of humble pie, and Alexis gets an unexpected offer.
episodes.title: Moira's Nudes

episodes.synopsis: In need of votes, Moira attempts to woo a key demographic. Alexis realizes her job is no cakewalk, and David takes on a terrifying responsibility.
episodes.title: Ronnie's Party

episodes.synopsis: Johnny and Moira's routine is upset when a new guest comes to the motel. Meanwhile, Alexis and David dream about a new place to live.
episodes.title: The Motel Guest

episodes.synopsis: After Moira's campaign signs go missing, she instantly suspects the worst. Meanwhile, when David's career suffers a setback, Alexis tries to help.
episodes.title: Lawn Signs

episodes.synopsis: Johnny and Moira's anniversary celebration takes a surprising twist. Meanwhile, Alexis and David do a little self-reflection at Mutt's party.
episodes.title: Happy Anniversary

episodes.synopsis: A new business venture vexes Johnny, Moira dives headfirst into local politics, and David suffers an uncomfortable familial encounter.
episodes.title: Opening Night

episodes.synopsis: Johnny's good deed puts him in a bad spot, Alexis and Moira plan a reluctant lunch date, and David and Stevie enter negotiations.
episodes.title: The Throuple

episodes.synopsis: Johnny and Moira devise an elaborate ruse to look even more broke than they are. David helps Stevie lay her great-aunt to rest.
episodes.title: New Car

episodes.synopsis: David's crippling test anxiety is hurting his chances for a new driver's license. Johnny and Moira try to dissuade Stevie from selling the motel.
episodes.title: Driving Test

episodes.synopsis: David helps Moira prepare for a film audition, Johnny rents out motel rooms by the hour, and Alexis sees more than she should.
episodes.title: Rooms by the Hour

episodes.synopsis: Johnny and Stevie try to reach a partnership with the local golf course. Moira attempts to recruit guests for Twyla's murder mystery party.
episodes.title: Murder Mystery

episodes.synopsis: David considers starting a new business, Alexis goes back to high school, and Johnny gives Ivan the baker some romantic advice.
episodes.title: General Store

episodes.synopsis: Johnny's custom coasters come under fire, Moira tries to help Stevie with the guests, and David makes a new acquaintance.
episodes.title: Motel Review

episodes.synopsis: Nobody's using the car's sign-out sheet, much to Johnny's dismay. Moira and Roland attend a conference. Alexis is smitten with Patrick.
episodes.title: The Affair

episodes.synopsis: An ex-boyfriend of David arrives to do a photo shoot with Moira. Johnny and Roland join Bob's poker game. Alexis gets some surprising news.
episodes.title: Sebastien Raine

episodes.synopsis: Alexis infects the motel with head lice. Moira is distressed to hear the town wants to name a flower garden after her.
episodes.title: Stop Saying Lice!

episodes.synopsis: A family portrait's overwhelming size poses problems. David hosts a soft launch of his business. Alexis and Ted share a moment.
episodes.title: Friends & Family

episodes.synopsis: Johnny and Stevie celebrate a fully booked motel, Alexis graduates from high school and David and Patrick hit the town.
episodes.title: Grad Night

episodes.synopsis: Finally, the motel is completely booked -- but the landmark occasion is jeopardized when Stevie finds a dead body in room 4.
episodes.title: Dead Guy in Room 4

episodes.synopsis: When Johnny finds a positive pregnancy test in Alexis's garbage, he sits her down for a talk, not knowing she's got something else on her mind.
episodes.title: Pregnancy Test

episodes.synopsis: Moira prepares for her one-woman show at Asbestos Fest. David and Patrick disagree on how to deal with a group of loitering teens.
episodes.title: Asbestos Fest

episodes.synopsis: Alexis and Twyla hit the town for a girls' night. Meanwhile, David is made aware that sometimes he can be just a smidge stubborn.
episodes.title: Girls’ Night

episodes.synopsis: The rumors of Moira Rose's death are greatly exaggerated online. Roland makes Johnny an offer he'd really like to refuse.
episodes.title: RIP Moira Rose

episodes.synopsis: David and Patrick host an open mic night in hopes of drawing customers to Rose Apothecary. Meanwhile, Alexis offers the motel her marketing insights.
episodes.title: Open Mic

episodes.synopsis: As Alexis seeks help in deciphering a text message from Ted, Johnny and Moira plan a family barbecue as a way to get to know Patrick.
episodes.title: The Barbecue

episodes.synopsis: Johnny becomes the newest Jazzagal. David and Stevie play the long con at a honeymoon resort. Alexis dips her toe into the online dating pool.
episodes.title: The Jazzaguy

episodes.synopsis: David starts to regret not making nice with Patrick sooner. Alexis and Moira accidentally think alike. Johnny's gift to Stevie isn't well received.
episodes.title: The Olive Branch

episodes.synopsis: Alexis has an intriguing encounter with an old friend. David agrees to throw Jocelyn a baby shower. Johnny and Moira conduct unconventional research.
episodes.title: Baby Sprinkle

episodes.synopsis: The motel's big rebranding rollout is thrown off course when the bath supplies from Rose Apothecary start causing problems. Moira has jury duty.
episodes.title: The Rollout

episodes.synopsis: As Schitt's Creek's first annual singles week gets underway, Patrick tells David exactly how he feels, and the town population grows by one.
episodes.title: Singles Week

episodes.synopsis: Johnny's eager to throw a good old-fashioned Christmas party. However, other members of the Rose family are decidedly less enthused.
episodes.title: Merry Christmas, Johnny Rose

episodes.synopsis: And, action! Moira's in Bosnia, making a film she hopes will resurrect her acting career. Meanwhile, David and Alexis enjoy the great outdoors.
episodes.title: The Crowening

episodes.synopsis: Moira frets over a pile of old love letters addressed to her one and only. David and Stevie contend with an armed stickup.
episodes.title: Love Letters

episodes.synopsis: How to best impress a hotel reviewer? Johnny and Alexis have a plan. Also, David and Patrick look for a new apartment.
episodes.title: The Plant

episodes.synopsis: Glamour has a price and Johnny's not sure he can afford it. Meanwhile, a reluctant David hits the open road with Stevie.
episodes.title: The Dress

episodes.synopsis: As David and Patrick throw themselves a housewarming party, Moira and Johnny struggle with a monumental task: babysitting Roland Jr.
episodes.title: Housewarming

episodes.synopsis: Jocelyn enjoys a night out at the casino, courtesy of Moira and the Jazzagals. Johnny sits Stevie down for an awkward chat.
episodes.title: Rock On!

episodes.synopsis: Johnny suspects that Ted's mom has a thing for him -- a "whisper of desire," if you will. Meanwhile, Moira can't resist the call of the stage.
episodes.title: A Whisper of Desire

episodes.synopsis: While Johnny and Stevie attend the prestigious regional hospitality awards, Moira strives to stop Alexis from trying out for "Cabaret."
episodes.title: The Hospies

episodes.synopsis: David agrees to play in an annual baseball game. Also, Stevie learns that Moira's rehearsals can be rather hard to take.
episodes.title: The M.V.P

episodes.synopsis: Johnny and Moira accidentally hit a cat. David bumps into an old acquaintance who's launching a business that sounds a lot like Rose Apothecary.
episodes.title: Roadkill

episodes.synopsis: Alexis brings Moira to a soap opera convention. Patrick's parents come to Schitt's Creek for his surprise party.
episodes.title: Meet the Parents

episodes.synopsis: Johnny steps in for Moira at the annual mayor's roast. Meanwhile, David does his best to keep his mom from discovering Stevie and Patrick's secret.
episodes.title: The Roast

episodes.synopsis: Patrick brings David on a romantic hike. Johnny's health scare puts an even bigger scare into the rest of the Roses.
episodes.title: The Hike

episodes.synopsis: Overture, curtain, lights -- this is it, the night of nights! Opening night for "Cabaret" has arrived, but Stevie the star is nowhere to be found.
episodes.title: Life Is a Cabaret

episodes.synopsis: Alexis is elated about visiting Ted — but there's an issue. David and Patrick scout a potential wedding venue, and Moira has a realization.
episodes.title: Smoke Signals

episodes.synopsis: David is horrified when one of his childhood issues returns. Meanwhile, Moira — with an assist from Alexis — promotes "Crows" on social media.
episodes.title: The Incident

episodes.synopsis: David and Stevie compete for a chance to "see the world," Johnny gets some bad news at the bank, and Alexis searches for a way to stay close to Ted.
episodes.title: The Job Interview

episodes.synopsis: After sharing the trailer to "Crows," Moira is disturbed by Jocelyn's less-than-rapturous response. Also, Johnny and Roland conduct a stakeout.
episodes.title: Maid of Honour

episodes.synopsis: Alexis plans Moira's red carpet movie premiere. Patrick shares his relationship goals with David. Stevie reconsiders life at the motel.
episodes.title: The Premiere

episodes.synopsis: Johnny volunteers to help Bob with dating. Alexis and Moira put a positive spin on the premiere fiasco. David and Patrick consider an ex's invitation.
episodes.title: The Wingman

episodes.synopsis: While Moira and David sample some wine, Johnny tries to have a man-to-man chat with Patrick, and Alexis lends her PR expertise to an exercise guru.
episodes.title: Moira Rose

episodes.synopsis: Alexis gets a pleasant surprise, David gets an unpleasant surprise, and Johnny and Moira cut the ribbon — well, basically — on their new motel.
episodes.title: The Presidential Suite

episodes.synopsis: Johnny gets overly involved with Alexis's love life, David takes on a new employee, and Moira learns her magazine interview ruffled a few feathers.
episodes.title: Rebound

episodes.synopsis: Johnny frets about how to pay for David's increasingly opulent wedding while Moira meets-and-greets a soap opera producer from her past.
episodes.title: Sunrise, Sunset

episodes.synopsis: Can David and Patrick escape their bachelor party? Will Moira muster the energy for voiceover work? Will Johnny's phone ever ring? Answers await!
episodes.title: The Bachelor Party

episodes.synopsis: Johnny, Stevie and Roland head to New York City to pitch their big idea while Moira, David and Alexis anxiously ponder the possibilities of a move.
episodes.title: The Pitch

episodes.synopsis: Moira strives to bounce back from unexpected news. Twyla shares a secret with Alexis. David and Patrick wrestle with the idea of home.
episodes.title: Start Spreading the News

episodes.synopsis: Rain! Cancellations! Untoward issues with the masseuse! David and Patrick's wedding day arrives — and with it, drama.
episodes.title: Happy Ending
